<item>
            <title>[LU-726] Test failure on test suite conf-sanity, subtest test_23a</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-726</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for bobijam &amp;lt;bobijam@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/5833b326-e573-11e0-9909-52540025f9af&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/5833b326-e573-11e0-9909-52540025f9af&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_23a failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;test failed to respond and timed out&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the std_out log shows that client print &quot;waiting for mount to finish ...&quot; only once, while the test is supposed to try 30 times and print that msg 30 times.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;11:15:33:Starting client: fat-intel-1vm1.lab.whamcloud.com: -o user_xattr,acl fat-intel-1vm3@tcp:/lustre /mnt/lustre
11:15:37:mount pid is 14088, mount.lustre pid is 14089
11:15:37:  PID TTY          TIME CMD
11:15:37:14089 ?        00:00:00 mount.lustre
11:15:37:  PID TTY          TIME CMD
11:15:37:waiting for mount to finish
11:15:37:root      1864     1  0 09:10 ?        00:00:00 automount
11:15:37:root     14088 14087  0 11:15 ?        00:00:00 mount -t lustre -o user_xattr,acl fat-intel-1vm3@tcp:/lustre /mnt/lustre
11:15:37:root     14089 14088  0 11:15 ?        00:00:00 /sbin/mount.lustre fat-intel-1vm3@tcp:/lustre /mnt/lustre -o rw,user_xattr,acl
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
